thread.title: William Brisko

author: William Brisko
title: William Brisko
text:
Since most of the components on my PCBs were from either DigiKey or Mouser (Arrow in the future), it would have been easier to get everything from them, including Coilcraft coils.
However, ordering direct was easy, pricing was tolerable, no minimums, and they even came on a reel (which is nice!) They were the first parts through the receiving door.
What can I say bad?
